name: cross-jurisdiction-journey-visualizer
description: >
  Animated data visualization showing how business, professional, and civic
  journeys flow through federal, state, and local government jurisdictions.
  114 journeys across 15 categories, 61 PLC node types, 3 jurisdiction levels.
  Built with USWDS v3 + D3.js as a static single-page app for GitHub Pages.
tags:
  - catalyst
  - permitting
  - licensing
  - visualization
  - d3js
  - uswds
  - government
  - stakeholder-communication
stack:
  - uswds-v3
  - d3js-v7
  - vanilla-js
  - static-html
deploy: github-pages
entry: index.html
